{#-
State dossier page skeleton (Constitution III.13 / Amendment W).

Mirrors county.md.j2 exactly, for the state nesting tier (Program 24 P2
WO-16, design canon R7 Victoria-3 nesting). Deliberately prose-free: this is
a scaffold page, not narrative copy. Every value interpolated here is a
plain string already resolved by babylon.projection.vault.render_state
(never a raw Optional StateView field — Jinja's StrictUndefined only fires
on genuinely *absent* names, and a present-but-None field renders the
literal text "None" rather than raising, so render_state.py precomputes
statblock_rows/absent_fields and the template only ever touches those and
the three always-present identity fields).

Fenced directives only ({statblock}/{absence}), matching
babylon.tui.directives.BabylonFence dispatch (ADR099: paired containers
break the 8.2.8 markdown walker).
-#}
